02:02:44.750 --> 02:02:48.540
so one of the challenges is
how much we can have some sort

02:02:48.540 --> 02:02:51.340
of shared terminology
while still recognizing

02:02:51.340 --> 02:02:53.230
that there are nuances in there.

02:02:53.230 --> 02:02:57.500
But yes, in order to share we do
need to do that, but the data needs

02:02:57.500 --> 02:03:02.430
