02:03:02.430 --> 02:03:04.890
So for example, I may
be using something

02:03:04.890 --> 02:03:08.210
in a completely different
way to Joe or Michele,

02:03:08.210 --> 02:03:11.380
but as long as that data is in a
structure that they can extract

02:03:11.380 --> 02:03:14.330
and reuse then I think that's
the critical component.

