02:05:08.170 --> 02:05:13.120
one is called scientific diagnostic

02:05:13.120 --> 02:05:16.940
for art historians,
which is very nice.

02:05:16.940 --> 02:05:21.360
It's a sort of [inaudible]
you could say

02:05:21.360 --> 02:05:31.150
so you know what [inaudible] was,
it was trying to teach to the son

02:05:31.150 --> 02:05:39.650
of the King of France whose formal
title was the [inaudible] of course

02:05:39.650 --> 02:05:46.530
and try to explain that in an
easier way and the very basic

02:05:46.530 --> 02:05:53.170 position:56%
of all the subjects for the cultures
